{"tid":2176672,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一次覺得自己就死既經歷","createTime":"2020-08-27T08:34:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T05:41:08.000Z","uid":187192,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"989c9f0cf7b32f36f6a2713367e03609dd4bae51","tid":2176672,"uid":187192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T08:34:55.000Z","msg":"早排睇發燒睇急症<br />\n點知佢叫我留院check下 期間做左幾次肺炎test又照左肺<br />\n到左下晏佢叫我照多次肺同做多個test <br />\n話我個肺有花..嚇到仆街 成晚訓唔著係度睇走馬燈<br />\n結果係淋巴發炎食左抗生素走得 我問佢個肺花成點 佢話無野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd2a20eac0defff595d26dee8799cc19a5e09418","tid":2176672,"uid":79793,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T08:36:41.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">樓下全部人唔好講發夢野</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1cf0f83397efa3ee34d5ffd154aedc7e0e285069","tid":2176672,"uid":187192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd2a20eac0defff595d26dee8799cc19a5e09418","tid":2176672,"uid":79793,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T08:36:41.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">樓下全部人唔好講發夢野</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T08:38:28.000Z","msg":"健康台講健康野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf3e15a89f475823d321c21ba525183a0d00578","tid":2176672,"uid":201274,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T08:49:23.000Z","msg":"細個想試下打丁咩感覺，係張床到打，不斷chok，chok到就射前既一秒，唔敢大大力射出黎，就用包皮包住個龜頭，再摙住層包皮，一黎想令佢唔會射出黎，二黎想用痛覺黎掩蓋個爽快感。<br />\n<br />\n第二朝起身發現條野條巨龍生左啲紅點，好驚就咁廢左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4420eda6d74d79c9f464724b0d97af605a766d8","tid":2176672,"uid":71930,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T09:34:15.000Z","msg":"驚恐症發作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12fbf55ae3a20ba5381e95c69405cf24f1bc5b91","tid":2176672,"uid":13149,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T09:40:05.000Z","msg":"打化療個陣 打到第9次藥物過敏<br />\n成個人出紅疹，心跳跳到190幾 ,咽喉腫哂呼吸唔到<br />\n要即刻急救打止敏針同聞氧氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚇死我 個陣全部姑娘即刻衝埋黎推我上床<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7363876db290aebce5ecc98e043147a93c287fce","tid":2176672,"uid":150483,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:03:21.000Z","msg":"自己一個係屋企<br />\n之後飲完酒去沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暈咗一陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"799ee9bf9a89df2e851ef93567c77f0236c5191f","tid":2176672,"uid":74850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:20:11.000Z","msg":"架貨車衝紅燈 我一隻腳踏出左馬路 拎轉頭睇到架貨車就埋線都唔慢速 我停左半拍 個人挨後 收返隻腳埋黎 然後架車係我身前刷過"},{"pid":"f272de6ab18d0098609f8bcf2514fc0a54fa8ec1","tid":2176672,"uid":187192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"799ee9bf9a89df2e851ef93567c77f0236c5191f","tid":2176672,"uid":74850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:20:11.000Z","msg":"架貨車衝紅燈 我一隻腳踏出左馬路 拎轉頭睇到架貨車就埋線都唔慢速 我停左半拍 個人挨後 收返隻腳埋黎 然後架車係我身前刷過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T13:03:52.000Z","msg":"我都試過 同個fd過緊十字路口 明明果個位綠燈行人唔比車轉 我見到就邊玩電話邊過 點知有架貨車轉緊過黎 好彩個fd拉住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1794f01a930bbadfaddcc30dd555276ca67045be","tid":2176672,"uid":251843,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T13:04:57.000Z","msg":"連續一個星期唔夠瞓同埋好大壓力 朝早又冇胃口冇食過嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住體力勞動 係咁比人要求重做 做做下突然之間好想嘔 瘋狂標冷汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要扒低休息 耳鳴同埋feel到天旋地轉 意識好模糊 身邊啲人見到我唔對路之後都即刻叫我食嘢 但超想嘔食唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />昏迷咗半個鐘之後冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3890e5f527e8c16c5b8be6ad6d8eb79ca0a3d8a","tid":2176672,"uid":167007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T13:13:05.000Z","msg":"失戀"},{"pid":"2df95354261d83ff38f625b972801e343ad7c453","tid":2176672,"uid":121742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T13:21:12.000Z","msg":"揸電單車去崖邊睇風景 諗住煞掣點知扭錯油門 好在停得切"},{"pid":"e0f3671847916270b366305a1b0fb9a3fe273e27","tid":2176672,"uid":138834,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T13:26:36.000Z","msg":"試過三樓跌落街，試過俾車撞到，試過啲壁佈板跌落嚟打中頭，試過揸帆船出到海打九號波，試過一條友行山半個人跌出懸崖，試落零下廿度雪國鄉下蕩失路，試過三十樓棚架踩斷竹，試過磨砂機爆碟碎片中頸，試過車床夾到手指，試過踩單車衝落山個brake壞左，試過揸電單車炒車...<br />\n<br />\n有時我會覺得人係不死之身<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e46c6906f3948d6c5963f2ae7666222d139c827","tid":2176672,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0f3671847916270b366305a1b0fb9a3fe273e27","tid":2176672,"uid":138834,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T13:26:36.000Z","msg":"試過三樓跌落街，試過俾車撞到，試過啲壁佈板跌落嚟打中頭，試過揸帆船出到海打九號波，試過一條友行山半個人跌出懸崖，試落零下廿度雪國鄉下蕩失路，試過三十樓棚架踩斷竹，試過磨砂機爆碟碎片中頸，試過車床夾到手指，試過踩單車衝落山個brake壞左，試過揸電單車炒車...<br />\n<br />\n有時我會覺得人係不死之身<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T13:28:59.000Z","msg":"我係你呢世唔再出街"},{"pid":"6384de23738d538c23d1c9dbcc97a6034bbc7cb6","tid":2176672,"uid":254600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T13:32:41.000Z","msg":"小時起馬路邊個球場打波，點知個波出左場去到馬路，無睇清楚就出左馬路執波，就起抬頭果下，架的士就起正我條腰側輕輕碰了一下"},{"pid":"66db72b032fdf89432d0ee7e8c35117392bef4d3","tid":2176672,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e46c6906f3948d6c5963f2ae7666222d139c827","tid":2176672,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0f3671847916270b366305a1b0fb9a3fe273e27","tid":2176672,"uid"