n嘩企左一陣已經feel到眼前開始變白而且呼吸同心跳加速<br />\n到夠鐘果下已經冇辦法行兩步去撳 麻煩左行過嘅助理姨姨幫手撳<br />\n結果我bp跌到勁低心跳超快 果下即刻坐左落床成個人勁panic 覺得自己差少少就要暈低<br />\n<br />\n仲有一次係醫院做果個跑步test 心跳去到190 覺得自己就黎往生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a510919ca001d804bb759b96037c9c184c41e2","tid":2176672,"uid":21924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T14:59:49.000Z","msg":"外國行山盪失路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3161abfe60a4be212208276ac2f9d4e347dc91","tid":2176672,"uid":39470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T15:04:57.000Z","msg":"行行下超市聽到巨響<br />\n然後見到D人個個望曬過黎<br />\n<br />\n原來我身後面有個貨架成個冧左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行慢少少都死撚左"},{"pid":"32dac2bb7ae48417bf623a4708be7297eaba34d1","tid":2176672,"uid":223672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T15:34:56.000Z","msg":"抑鬱症最嚴重個陣時食咗百幾粒精神科藥<br />\n個人迷迷糊糊仲係咁有幻覺幻聽<br />\n以為自己會死 醒返仲失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}